{"tid":2096621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：暫不屌柒加方暫停與香港引渡條約 稱保留屌鳩柒你的權利","createTime":"2020-07-06T08:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T08:56:36.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7177db8c7bc898feb7b0b72237318547266e50f4","tid":2096621,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"北京就加方暫停與香港引渡條約保留反應權利<br />\n發佈時間 2020-07-06 16:21<br />\n<br />\n中方強烈譴責加拿大暫停與香港的引渡條約，以及禁止向香港出口敏感軍事物品，強調會保留作出進一步反應的權利，一切後果完全由加方承擔。外交部發言人趙立堅指，加拿大的決定罔顧港區國安法有助「一國兩制」行穩致遠的基本事實，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，粗暴干涉中國內政。 中方敦促加拿大立即糾正錯誤，停止以任何方式干涉香港事務和中國內政，以免對中加關係造成進一步的損害<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345617&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=b9ecae00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345617</a>"},{"pid":"1e8bb46e1983ccd2e374944b2d8ac03889cf899c","tid":2096621,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"加拿大：咁你放棄咗嗰班年輕人 我都唔客氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0266d5e6d054410ac18991400fd088da4cc6788","tid":2096621,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"簡直要多謝天朝不屌之恩啦"},{"pid":"02975fa2408df4beb4cc7dce63297d3f6b99cd42","tid":2096621,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"你暫停加拿大同香港嘅引渡條約<br />\n我取消中國同你加拿大嘅引渡條約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc68c40f616256ccebe3fc2861670fef0c83efbf","tid":2096621,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"保留反應權利，發明新詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffaff483bbd90f7afccc9bf760a9895054ff750","tid":2096621,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"